						</outline>
					<outline text="You &lt;i&gt;must&lt;/i&gt; have seen this coming from a mile away. :-)" created="Tue, 02 Jul 2013 14:19:37 GMT" pgfnum="27531" type="link" url="http://static.scripting.com/myReallySimple/2013/07/02/davecast2013jul02.m4a"/>
					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://fargo.io/river.html&quot;&gt;http://fargo.io/river.html&lt;/a&gt;" created="Tue, 02 Jul 2013 14:19:46 GMT" pgfnum="27532"/>
					<outline text="After blogs, comes a river. Of course!" created="Tue, 02 Jul 2013 14:19:48 GMT" pgfnum="27533"/>
					<outline text="I put together a list of some of the &lt;a href=&quot;http://fargo.io/&quot;&gt;Fargo&lt;/a&gt; blogs I'm reading, added it to &lt;a href=&quot;http://river3.opml.org/&quot;&gt;River3&lt;/a&gt;, and let it churn for a while." created="Tue, 02 Jul 2013 14:19:57 GMT" pgfnum="27534"/>
					<outline text="I then did a little customizing of the CSS, imported a &lt;a href=&quot;http://bootswatch.com/&quot;&gt;Bootswatch&lt;/a&gt; theme, because everything we do is &lt;a href=&quot;http://twitter.github.io/bootstrap/&quot;&gt;Bootstrap&lt;/a&gt;, that was easy, and now I have a beautiful little river I can use (and so can you) to keep an eye on what our little nascent blogging community is doing." created="Tue, 02 Jul 2013 14:20:16 GMT" pgfnum="27535"/>
					<outline text="Of course it's &lt;i&gt;all&lt;/i&gt; a &lt;a href=&quot;http://scripting.com/davenet/2000/11/30/bootstrapping.html&quot;&gt;bootstrap&lt;/a&gt;. " created="Tue, 02 Jul 2013 14:23:38 GMT" pgfnum="27537"/>
					<outline text="Enjoy! :-)" created="Tue, 02 Jul 2013 14:21:14 GMT" pgfnum="27536"/>
					<outline text="PS: Here's a &lt;a href=&quot;http://static.scripting.com/myReallySimple/2013/07/02/davecast2013jul02.m4a&quot;&gt;9-minute podcast&lt;/a&gt; about all this michegas! :-)" created="Tue, 02 Jul 2013 14:58:33 GMT" pgfnum="27538"/>
					</outline>
