						<outline text="Update: I created my &lt;a href=&quot;http://davew.quora.com/Im-dreaming-of-a-White-Christmas&quot;&gt;own blog&lt;/a&gt; on Quora. It was easy. " created="Wed, 23 Jan 2013 22:40:35 GMT" pgfnum="17663"/>
