					<outline text="Peter Rojas of gdgt had an &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/peterrojas/status/291956766831423490&quot;&gt;interesting idea&lt;/a&gt;. Why not start a feed of the icons. Indeed. :-)" created="Thu, 17 Jan 2013 21:39:21 GMT" pgfnum="17310"/>
					<outline text="&lt;a href=&quot;http://static.scripting.com/myReallySimple/myTwitterIcon.xml&quot;&gt;http://static.scripting.com/myReallySimple/myTwitterIcon.xml&lt;/a&gt;" created="Thu, 17 Jan 2013 21:39:44 GMT" pgfnum="17312"/>
					<outline text="I can't add something to the feed without it going out to all my followers, so I'm not going to put the old icons in there. For that, here's a &lt;a href=&quot;https://dl.dropbox.com/u/36518280/misc/twitterIcons.zip&quot;&gt;zip archive&lt;/a&gt;. " created="Thu, 17 Jan 2013 21:39:40 GMT" pgfnum="17311"/>
