					<outline text="Famous TV actors from &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lane_Pryce&quot;&gt;Mad Men&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Breaking_Bad_characters#Gale_Boetticher&quot;&gt;Breaking Bad&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anita_Van_Buren&quot;&gt;Law &amp; Order&lt;/a&gt;. Surprising and fun to see them in 19th century costumes. " created="Tue, 13 Nov 2012 22:47:09 GMT" pgfnum="15365"/>
